hr.fer.zemris.java.custom.collections

Class ArrayIndexedCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • hr.fer.zemris.java.custom.collections.Collection
      • hr.fer.zemris.java.custom.collections.ArrayIndexedCollection

  • public class ArrayIndexedCollection
extends Collection
    Class represents resizable array-backed collection of objects. Duplicate elements are allowed, storage of null references is not allowed.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Toni Martinčić
